Dr. Reznick.

792
00:34:57,796 --> 00:35:00,065
Any thoughts?

793
00:35:00,098 --> 00:35:02,568
I don't think I can
fairly offer an opinion,

794
00:35:02,601 --> 00:35:04,936
because my career
could hang in the balance.

795
00:35:04,970 --> 00:35:07,306
Yeah, well, none of us
are disinterested parties,

796
00:35:07,339 --> 00:35:10,909
given the hospital's
reputation is also at stake.

797
00:35:10,942 --> 00:35:12,478
Did you screw up?

798
00:35:12,511 --> 00:35:14,246
Could that crisis
have been avoided?

799
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:17,015
♪♪

800
00:35:17,048 --> 00:35:21,320
If it could have been,
then we are all responsible.

801
00:35:21,353 --> 00:35:23,255
We were watching
everything she was doing,

802
00:35:23,289 --> 00:35:25,291
and none of us told her to stop.

803
00:35:26,792 --> 00:35:28,460
This is an easy call.

804
00:35:28,494 --> 00:35:30,929
There's only one reason
to tell her everything,

805
00:35:30,962 --> 00:35:33,332
and that's you might
feel guilty if you don't.

806
00:35:33,365 --> 00:35:36,034
On the other hand, there's
the future of this hospital.

807
00:35:36,067 --> 00:35:38,069
♪♪

808
00:35:45,777 --> 00:35:46,778
Okay.

809
00:35:47,713 --> 00:35:48,980
♪♪

810
00:35:49,014 --> 00:35:52,918
Shaun, if the patient asks
for details about the surgery,

811
00:35:52,951 --> 00:35:54,986
can you limit your answers?

812
00:35:55,020 --> 00:35:57,088
♪♪

813
00:35:57,523 --> 00:35:59,658
I... don't know.

814
00:36:00,859 --> 00:36:01,993
Okay, we need to know if...

815
00:36:02,027 --> 00:36:03,895
No.

816
00:36:03,929 --> 00:36:07,366
Dr. Murphy, I hope
you will limit your answers.

817
00:36:07,399 --> 00:36:09,535
But I won't order you
to defy your conscience.

818
00:36:09,568 --> 00:36:11,537
♪♪

819
00:36:20,479 --> 00:36:24,450
We don't normally have
patients share rooms, but...

820
00:36:24,483 --> 00:36:27,286
She's...?
Gonna be completely fine.

821
00:36:27,319 --> 00:36:30,256
And once she's recuperated,
we'll begin her on statins and Ezetimibe,

822
00:36:30,289 --> 00:36:32,491
and she'll undergo
lipid apheresis.

823
00:36:32,524 --> 00:36:33,792
It's kind of like dialysis,

824
00:36:33,825 --> 00:36:36,995
but it'll allow us to
extract LDL out of her blood.

825
00:36:37,028 --> 00:36:39,164
Should get her cholesterol
to within normal range.

826
00:36:40,832 --> 00:36:43,369
She'll need those drugs
and that other stuff

827
00:36:43,402 --> 00:36:44,470
for the rest of her life?

828
00:36:44,503 --> 00:36:48,006
Yes. But hopefully
a very long one.

829
00:36:49,408 --> 00:36:51,943
(EXHALES SHARPLY)

830
00:36:51,977 --> 00:36:53,979
(SNIFFLES) Thank you so much.

831
00:36:54,780 --> 00:36:56,482
Thank God I did what I did.

832
00:36:56,515 --> 00:36:58,417
(CHUCKLES)

833
00:36:58,450 --> 00:37:00,452
♪♪

834
00:37:08,059 --> 00:37:10,061
(CHUCKLES)

835
00:37:12,097 --> 00:37:15,166
KAYLEY: (NORMAL VOICE)
Everything went great?

836
00:37:15,200 --> 00:37:17,403
(SIGHS) The repair was successful.
You should have no...

837
00:37:17,436 --> 00:37:20,071
KAYLEY: Everything went great.
Say it. Say it to your fans.

838
00:37:21,607 --> 00:37:23,842
Everything went great.
(KAYLEY GIGGLES)

