00:37:30,782 --> 00:37:33,785
She was lead surgeon
in a successful...

843
00:37:33,819 --> 00:37:35,421
KAYLEY: And how gorgeous
is that hair?

844
00:37:35,454 --> 00:37:38,189
Dr. Morgan Reznick, take a bow!

845
00:37:40,292 --> 00:37:41,860
(KAYLEY LAUGHS)

846
00:37:41,893 --> 00:37:44,062
KAYLEY: She was wrist-deep
all up in my mouth, y'all.

847
00:37:44,095 --> 00:37:45,731
She is a damn hero!

848
00:37:45,764 --> 00:37:46,898
(KAYLEY LAUGHS)

849
00:37:48,567 --> 00:37:50,201
You've got work to do.

850
00:37:50,235 --> 00:37:51,236
We're proud of you.

851
00:37:54,673 --> 00:37:56,508
Any reason you screwed up?

852
00:37:56,542 --> 00:37:58,810
I didn't. It could've
happened to anyone.

853
00:37:58,844 --> 00:38:01,347
Not anyone suffers
from arthritic pain.

854
00:38:01,380 --> 00:38:02,881
That didn't affect anything.

855
00:38:02,914 --> 00:38:04,550
You sure about that?

856
00:38:04,583 --> 00:38:05,751
'Cause I'm not.

