867
00:38:53,632 --> 00:38:54,966
I was jealous.

868
00:38:57,035 --> 00:38:59,671
And it's something
that I have to work out.

869
00:38:59,705 --> 00:39:01,740
♪♪

870
00:39:02,508 --> 00:39:05,644
